---
description: '{{skill.name}} — {{skill.description}}'
---

<skill-activation>
{{#if (eq skill.phase "core")}}
1. LOAD the FULL skill file from {project-root}/.forge/core/{{skill.slug}}/SKILL.md
{{else}}
1. LOAD the FULL skill file from {project-root}/.forge/skills/{{skill.phase}}/{{skill.slug}}/SKILL.md
{{/if}}
2. READ its entire contents and follow the instructions
3. LOAD runtime config from {project-root}/.forge/config.yaml
4. Execute the workflow as specified
</skill-activation>
